org.apache.iceberg.flink.source.split

Class SplitComparators

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iceberg.flink.source.split.SplitComparators

  • public class SplitComparators
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides implementations of SerializableComparator which could be used for ordering splits. These are used by the OrderedSplitAssignerFactory and the IcebergSourceReader
